<template>I think that there's too much pressure to make people conform, and Ithink that one man may be first-rate, but if you get one man andtwo second-rate men together then he's not going to be first-rate any longerbecause thethe voice of that majority will be asecond-rate voice. The behavior of that majority will be second-rate. And Ithink that a second-rate man [who stays] himself at least won'tbe third rate.</template></category>
