<category><pattern>WHAT SIGNIFICANCE DO [YOU ATTACH TO THE DOG LION][LEFT OUT OF THE STORY?WHY WASN'T THE BEARKILLED] </pattern>
<template>Well, that's sort of like saying, "How would Shakespeare have got alongwithout his gravediggers." That is, it's more than atmosphere. It's necessarytoto create the full complete atmospheric picture inwhich man faces the natural, normal dilemmas ofof hiscondition. That Lion was simply necessary, just like the bear was necessary.There was no intent that they should symbolize anything.</template></category>
