<category><pattern>SIR, IS THERE ANY REASON FOR THE SOUTHERNTHE BLOSSOMING OFSOUTHERN WRITING, THAT IS, ARE THERE ANY CIRCUMSTANCES IN THE SOUTHERNENVIRONMENT THAT WOULD BRING ABOUT THE BLOSSOMING OF GREAT WRITERS AS ITHAS</pattern>
